Textmate bundles:

1) Installing a bundle

	1) cd ~/Library/Application Support/TextMate/Bundles
	2) git clone git://github.com/fredoliveira/yui-css-textmate-bundle.git
	3) restart TextMate or Reload Bundles
	
2) Updating a bundle

	1) cd ~/Library/Application Support/TextMate/Bundles
	2) cd YUICSS.tmbundle
	3) git pull
	